      "instruction": "<p>While the breadcrumbs are cooking, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail and chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
