    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat the reserved pan with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1680016323213-x200.jpg",
