            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the courgette is nearly softened, add your <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>linguine</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>linguine</strong>, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1680016330695-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
