          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680016335096-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce is cooking, chop your<strong> basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once thickened, add the <strong>drained linguine</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>basil</strong> (save some for garnish!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy courgette linguine</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more starchy cooking water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
