            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1680016339587-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy courgette linguine</strong> topped with the <strong>walnut crumb</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped basil </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
